Package: silvR21
Title: Processing Tools for the Silva21 Project
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Michael Burnett
Maintainer: Michael Burnett <mdmbur19@mail.ubc.ca>
Description: This package was created for simplifying the means of acquiring climate data from ClimateNA. The default options are the selections used within Silva21.
    These funcitons are useful for preparing DEM files to be used with ClimateNA, access climate data, and processing the generated data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
